sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Entwickler
    participant DC as Docker Compose
    participant Runner as Quality Runner
    participant Repo as Projektdateien
    participant Out as quality_output
    participant Hub as Quality Hub

    Note over Entwickler,DC: Start des Quality-Profils
    Entwickler->>DC: docker compose --profile quality up --build
    DC->>Runner: Runner starten
    DC->>Hub: Hub starten

    Note over Runner,Repo: Quality Runner führt Checks aus
    activate Runner
    Runner->>Repo: Repository in Arbeitskopie kopieren
    Runner->>Runner: Backend-Checks ausführen
    Runner->>Runner: Frontend-Checks ausführen
    Runner->>Runner: Security-Checks ausführen
    Runner->>Runner: Playwright-E2E-Tests ausführen
    Runner->>Out: report.json, Logs und HTML-Reports schreiben
    deactivate Runner

    Note over Hub,Out: Ergebnisse im Hub anzeigen
    Hub->>Out: Ergebnisse lesen
    Out-->>Hub: Status, Logs und Reports
    Hub-->>Entwickler: Score, Checkliste und Reports anzeigen
